Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.15,0:00:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八千八聲 啼至血吐 杜鵑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.47,0:00:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說那種小鳥即便流著血也會繼續歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.91,0:00:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最重要的朋友也一直在歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.47,0:00:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊流血一邊歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想見你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然不能再見了 我不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,響
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我重要的朋友在戰場上一直歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.27,0:01:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來你現在在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經到會場了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉不能去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.23,0:01:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.23,0:01:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的Live可是未來約我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.83,0:01:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盛岡的奶奶受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸說現在開車去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對這裡不熟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也許被詛咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該說等不及呢 還是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不習慣開演前的這段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是想快點大搞一場的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這也無法隨心所欲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.31,0:02:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說翼你在緊張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.75,0:02:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻井女士也說今天很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.11,0:02:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太認真了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.11,0:02:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏 翼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦十郎老大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:02:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你們也許知道的 今天是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說很重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天Live的結果是賭上了人類的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙關照 我是櫻井了子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 馬上過去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞台上就交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 難題就交給老大和了子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就大幹一場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太認真了 翼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繃太緊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後很容易斷的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的拍檔是翼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼擺出這樣的表情的話 連我也高興不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不高興的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來Live的大家也不會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是挺明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奏一起的話總感覺會有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 奏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你集齊雙翼的ZweiWing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論多遠都能飛去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何事都能跨越
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心撲通直跳 視線無法轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Live啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Phonic Gain顯示了預料之內的延長率
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.91,0:07:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全設施支撐不了上升的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去聖遺物會啟動 不 是暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Noise來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Noise
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想死 我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 翼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡擁有長槍和劍的就只有我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.31,0:08:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令官還什麼都沒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,500)}{\3c&H192ABF&}Croitzal ronzell gungnir zizzl
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了子君 了子君 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青銅蛇之
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx70\fscy70\pos(310,312)}Nehushtan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時限式就到此為止了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我睜開眼 不要放棄活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:12:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想著哪天有機會能唱歌唱到身心疲憊為止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有這麼多傢伙來聽我們唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也不會吝嗇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你們最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕唱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,100)}{\3c&H192ABF&}Gatrandis babel ziggurat edenal
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,100)}{\3c&H192ABF&}Emustrolonzen finne enfarmati
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,100)}{\3c&H192ABF&}Gatrandis babel ziggurat edenal
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:13:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,500)}{\3c&H192ABF&}Emustrolonzen finne el zizzl
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 奏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能唱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能聽到歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 這是燃燒生命的終焉之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.67,0:13:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:54.91,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H00&\pos(320,320)\bord1}舞台回到\N現在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立花同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子爬上樹之後就不下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想會不會是餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立花同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺剛入學就連續高潮了一百次一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被詛咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一半都是因為響太笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的都是平時的多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說成樂於助人 樂於助人是我的興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,響的情況太過度了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說不會把課本借給同班同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.43,0:14:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來會給我看的所以沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CD發售日就是明天了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼小姐果然好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為仰慕翼小姐才報讀莉蒂安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是連影子也不曾一見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也知道人家是頂級藝人 不是那麼容易見得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天救了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是ZweiWing的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是出院後所聽到的新聞卻只說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏小姐和很多人都犧牲在世界災害Noise的手下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥中的ZweiWing那難道是幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以想見翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我感覺我知道那一天發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通兵器果然不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(100,500)}{\3c&HBF2A19&}lmyuteus amenohabakiri tron
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼 先和一課合作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀察對方的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我一個人沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.99,0:16:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由自衛隊特別災害對應機動部進行的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避難誘導已經完成 將危害控制到了最低限度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離這裡沒多遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 是風鳴翼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藝人氣場外露
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走近點看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡的歌姬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完完全全被翼小姐當成奇怪的孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正沒錯 所以沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個還要花一段時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 今天是翼小姐的CD發售日來著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.43,0:18:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這個年代還CD
